2. 

In these Regulations – 

“Act of 2023” means the Electricity Costs (Emergency Measures) Domestic 
Accounts Act 2023 (No. 29 of 2023); 

“first payment period” means the period referred to in paragraph (a) of the 
definition of payment period in section 1 of the Act of 2023; 

“second payment period” means the period referred to in paragraph (b) of the 
definition of payment period in section 1 of the Act of 2023; 

“third payment period” means the period referred to in paragraph (c) of the 
definition of payment period in section 1 of the Act of 2023.
